    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This absolute gem is in pristine condition and has been my pride and joy. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it honestly looks and drives like a dream! It's super clean, super smooth, and totally ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this well-loved\u2014come take a look and see for yourself, you're going to love it!",
