    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a flawless mechanical pedigree, including a documented VANOS service and proactive subframe reinforcement to maintain peak torsional rigidity. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, utilizing original dampers and bushings for an unadulterated driving feel. Finished in an immaculate coat with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, this unmodified example represents the zenith of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
