      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-quality masterpiece that has been fastidiously maintained and strictly garage-kept. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous paint with a professional-grade ceramic coating, showing absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of creases, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still retains its original new-car scent. Every technological feature and button operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a complete, documented service history and a clean title. It has recently passed a rigorous multi-point inspection with flying colors and sits on a fresh set of premium tires. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
