    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been incredibly careful with it, keeping it pampered and garage-parked. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and is ready for its next big adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
